      "meaning": "门页，构成门的一片。",
      "examples": [
        "推开门扇。",
        "一扇大门。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "扇"
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "摇动生风取凉的用具。",
      "examples": [
        "扇子很漂亮。",
        "她用扇子扇风。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "扇"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "板状或片状的屏，如门扇、隔扇。",
      "examples": [
